blurt 1.0 ShowPath.pm
===========================

A plugin for blurt 1.0 that displays the current category and the
current post title (if applicable) in head and foot templates.

By Matthijs de Jonge (rhmtts@gmail.com).

This software is public domain software: do with it whatever you want.


INSTALL:
========

- If you want, you can edit ShowPath.pm to change the separator placed
  before the category name and post title

- Upload ShowPath.pm to the plugins directory of your blurt
  installation on the server

VARIABLES:
==========

The ShowPath plugin supplies the following variables for use in all
templates:

$ShowPath::Category : the name of the current category
$ShowPath::PostName : the title of the current post

both are empty if not applicable.
